│ 1713 /// Inductions are modeled using the following sub-classes:                                                                                                 │
│ 1714 ///  * VPCanonicalIVPHIRecipe: Canonical scalar induction of the vector loop,                                                                               │
│ 1715 ///    starting at a specified value (zero for the main vector loop, the resume                                                                             │
│ 1716 ///    value for the epilogue vector loop) and stepping by 1. The induction                                                                                 │
│ 1717 ///    controls exiting of the vector loop by comparing against the vector trip                                                                             │
│ 1718 ///    count. Produces a single scalar PHI for the induction value per                                                                                      │
│ 1719 ///    iteration.                                                                                                                                           │
